PHASE 2 — PRESSURE & RHYTHM PIPELINE (REPO-READY)
INPUT
MacroGeographyPackage
+ Physical Layers:
  - elevation / relief
  - mountain barriers
  - hydrology (rivers, basins)
  - coastal morphology
  - volcanic zones
  - climate envelopes
  - ocean influence
  - route graph
  - chokepoints
  - isolation fields
PIPELINE (ЖЁСТКАЯ ПОСЛЕДОВАТЕЛЬНОСТЬ)
0. Normalization Layer

Задача: привести все поля к единому масштабу

normalize(field, 0..1)

Выход:

normalizedElevation
normalizedMoisture
normalizedAccessCost
normalizedIsolation
1. Climate Hostility Generator

Алгоритмы:

latitude bands
elevation penalty
ocean smoothing
wind exposure (если есть)
cold = f(latitude, elevation)
heat = f(latitude)
humidityStress = f(moisture variance)

Выход:

coldPressure
heatPressure
humidityPressure
2. Terrain Harshness Generator
harshness = slope + rockiness + fragmentation

Выход:

terrainPressure
3. Hydrology Stress Generator
waterAccess = riverDensity + basinPresence
variability = flood + drought cycles

Выход:

waterReliability
waterStress
4. Food Reliability Generator
fertility = soil + moisture + flatness
seasonalLoss = climate variance

Выход:

foodReliability
foodStress
5. Travel Exposure Generator
exposure =
  routeCost
+ terrainDifficulty
+ stormCorridors
+ chokepointDependency

Выход:

travelPressure
6. Isolation Burden Generator
isolation =
  accessCost
+ routeFragility
+ distanceToCore

Выход:

isolationPressure
7. Chokepoint Stress Generator
stress =
  trafficDensity
* routeDependency
* failureImpact

Выход:

chokepointPressure
8. Ecological Stability Generator
stability =
  regenerationRate
- extractionPressure
- climateVolatility

Выход:

ecologicalStability
ecologicalFragility
9. Catastrophe Susceptibility
catastrophe =
  volcanicRisk
+ stormFrequency
+ floodZones
+ droughtZones

Выход:

catastrophePressure
СБОРКА PRESSURE
10. Pressure Field Synthesis
PressureField = {
  survivabilityPressure,
  mobilityPressure,
  supplyPressure,
  isolationPressure,
  fragilityPressure,
  catastrophePressure
}
RHYTHM ЧАСТЬ
11. Seasonality Generator
seasonality =
  latitude
+ oceanInfluence
+ elevation
12. Storm Cadence Generator
stormCycle =
  ocean + wind + pressure gradients
13. Navigation Window Generator
navigation =
  inverse(stormCycle + ice + waves)
14. Scarcity Cycle Generator
scarcity =
  foodReliability fluctuation
+ water variability
15. Predictability Analyzer
predictability =
  variance of all cycles
16. Recovery Tempo Generator (КРИТИЧНО)
recovery =
  regenerationRate
- pressure load
17. Rhythm Synthesis
RhythmField = {
  seasonalityStrength,
  predictability,
  ruptureFrequency,
  scarcityCadence,
  navigationCadence,
  recoveryTempo
}
VALIDATION
18. Validation Layer

Проверки:

❌ нет равномерного давления
❌ нет одного ритма везде
❌ нет отсутствия recovery зон
❌ нет сломанной корреляции с географией
19. Selective Rebalance

Пересчитываются только:

climate
routes
cadence
OUTPUT
{
  PressureFieldPackage,
  EnvironmentalRhythmPackage,
  summaries
}